grants-ideas-ai-governance-after-ceo-threatened-pull-out-eu-over-regulation?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3222114_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="5b8593cc-c36f-4c3a-8851-86243db95042" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-bundle="article">OpenAI</a>的<a href="https://www.scmp.com/topics/chatgpt?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3222114_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="69f8b25a-1c45-422b-b67f-4ff6debd636b" data-entity-type="taxonomy_term" data-entity-bundle="topics">ChatGPT</a>背后的内容生成<a href="https://www.scmp.com/topics/technology?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3222114_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="1e10ae82-d07d-4c9d-9165-59e6bdc442a5" data-entity-type="taxonomy_term" data-entity-bundle="topics">技术</a>。</p><p>知乎是中国<a href="https://www.scmp.com/business/markets/article/3175162/zhihu-loses-one-fifth-market-value-sec-delisting-pressure-mars?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3222114_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="ba097648-ebb6-4846-a45c-eecbe46341f0" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-bundle="article">最大的知识共享平台运营商</a>，该公司首席技术官李大海在周六的一份报告中表示，将立即开始对名为“搜<em>所聚合</em>”的功能进行内部测试，该功能在英文中翻译为“搜索聚合”由国家支持的报纸科技日报。 </p><div class="meter__linear relative" id="default-meter-page-views-11"><img width="auto" height="1" src="https://www.scmp.com/images/1x1.png" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="dm__l3"><hr class="vertical-line"><div class="dm__lw"><svg class="dm__l" height="24" viewBox="0 0 18 24" width="18" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><g style="stroke:#000;fill:none;fill-rule:evenodd;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;stroke-width:1.5"><rect height="13.5" rx="1.5" width="16.5" x=".75" y="9.75"></rect><path d="m3.75 9.75v-3.75c0-2.89949494 2.35050506-5.25 5.25-5.25 2.8994949 0 5.25 2.35050506 5.25 5.25v3.75"></path><path d="m9.00000067 15.75c-.20710